{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-16",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_16_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "The Third Murder",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 1,
  "page_total": 5,
  "page_start_sec": 9.6,
  "page_end_sec": 276.2,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.545,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 9.6,
      "end": 10.3,
      "text": "CHAPTER XVI."
    },
    {
      "start": 10.656,
      "end": 12.0,
      "text": "SPADE went into the Hotel Sutter"
    },
    {
      "start": 12.0,
      "end": 13.96,
      "text": "and telephoned the Alexandria."
    },
    {
      "start": 14.816,
      "end": 15.72,
      "text": "Gutman was not in."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.64,
      "end": 17.54,
      "text": "No member of Gutman's"
    },
    {
      "start": 17.54,
      "end": 18.3,
      "text": "party was in."
    },
    {
      "start": 19.168,
      "end": 20.62,
      "text": "Spade telephoned the Belvedere."
    },
    {
      "start": 21.312,
      "end": 22.56,
      "text": "Cairo was not in,"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.68,
      "end": 24.4,
      "text": "had not been in that day."
    },
    {
      "start": 25.376,
      "end": 26.9,
      "text": "Spade went to his office.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 27.37,
      "end": 28.44,
      "text": "A swart",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 28.58,
      "end": 32.22,
      "text": "greasy man in notable clothes was waiting in the outer room."
    },
    {
      "start": 33.12,
      "end": 33.64,
      "text": "Effie Perine,"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.02,
      "end": 35.06,
      "text": "indicating the swart man,"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.24,
      "end": 35.52,
      "text": "said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.72,
      "end": 38.04,
      "text": "\"This gentleman wishes to see you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.12,
      "end": 38.3,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 38.48,
      "end": 38.84,
      "text": "Spade.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 39.936,
      "end": 42.2,
      "text": "Spade smiled and bowed and opened the inner door.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 42.98,
      "end": 43.26,
      "text": "\"Come in.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 44.44,
      "end": 45.6,
      "text": "Before following the man in"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.82,
      "end": 46.96,
      "text": "Spade asked Effie Perine:"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.22,
      "end": 49.04,
      "text": "\"Any news on that other matter?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 49.4,
      "end": 50.18,
      "text": "\"No,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 50.18,
      "end": 50.4,
      "text": "sir.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 50.77,
      "end": 53.52,
      "text": "The swart man was the proprietor",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 53.62,
      "end": 55.6,
      "text": "of a moving-picture-theater in Market Street."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.42,
      "end": 58.6,
      "text": "He suspected one of his cashiers and a doorman"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.84,
      "end": 60.3,
      "text": "of colluding to defraud him."
    },
    {
      "start": 61.408,
      "end": 62.88,
      "text": "Spade hurried him through the story,"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.16,
      "end": 64.62,
      "text": "promised to \"take care of it,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 65.152,
      "end": 66.8,
      "text": "asked for and received fifty dollars,"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.02,
      "end": 69.48,
      "text": "and got rid of him in less than half an hour."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.0,
      "end": 72.94,
      "text": "When the corridor-door had closed behind the showman",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 73.1,
      "end": 75.18,
      "text": "Effie Perine came into the inner office."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.64,
      "end": 78.02,
      "text": "Her sunburned face was worried and questioning."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.46,
      "end": 80.08,
      "text": "\"You haven't found her yet?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 80.28,
      "end": 81.02,
      "text": "she asked."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.22,
      "end": 82.06,
      "text": "He shook",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 82.16,
      "end": 84.08,
      "text": "his head and went on stroking his bruised"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.08,
      "end": 86.12,
      "text": "temple lightly in circles with his fingertips."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.24,
      "end": 87.86,
      "text": "\"How is it?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 87.88,
      "end": 88.54,
      "text": "she asked."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.54,
      "end": 89.9,
      "text": "\"All right,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 90.02,
      "end": 91.82,
      "text": "but I've got plenty of headache.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 92.9,
      "end": 94.18,
      "text": "She went around behind him,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 94.4,
      "end": 95.34,
      "text": "put his hand down,"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.42,
      "end": 97.6,
      "text": "and stroked his temple with her slender fingers."
    },
    {
      "start": 98.0,
      "end": 99.52,
      "text": "He leaned back until the"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.6,
      "end": 102.34,
      "text": "back of his head over the chair-top rested against her breast."
    },
    {
      "start": 103.14,
      "end": 103.48,
      "text": "He said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.6,
      "end": 104.76,
      "text": "\"You're an angel.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 105.84,
      "end": 108.88,
      "text": "She bent her head forward over his and looked down into his face.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 109.86,
      "end": 110.86,
      "text": "\"You've got to find her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.92,
      "end": 111.14,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 112.18,
      "end": 113.64,
      "text": "It's more than a day and she—\""
    },
    {
      "start": 113.64,
      "end": 116.46,
      "text": "He stirred and impatiently interrupted her:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 116.73,
      "end": 118.18,
      "text": "\"I haven't got to do"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.28,
      "end": 118.6,
      "text": "anything,"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.34,
      "end": 122.08,
      "text": "but if you'll let me rest this damned head a minute or two"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.24,
      "end": 123.78,
      "text": "I'll go out and find her.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 124.7,
      "end": 125.4,
      "text": "She murmured,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 125.98,
      "end": 126.58,
      "text": "\"Poor head,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 127.34,
      "end": 128.88,
      "text": "and stroked it in silence awhile."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.66,
      "end": 130.36,
      "text": "Then she asked:"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.02,
      "end": 132.08,
      "text": "\"You know where she is?"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.7,
      "end": 133.6,
      "text": "Have you any idea?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 133.94,
      "end": 135.76,
      "text": "The telephone-bell rang.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 136.864,
      "end": 138.42,
      "text": "Spade picked up the telephone and said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.56,
      "end": 138.82,
      "text": "\"Hello. . . ."
    },
    {
      "start": 139.27,
      "end": 140.02,
      "text": "Yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.02,
      "end": 140.28,
      "text": "Sid,"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.5,
      "end": 141.68,
      "text": "it came out all right,"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.68,
      "end": 142.0,
      "text": "thanks. . . ."
    },
    {
      "start": 142.92,
      "end": 143.2,
      "text": "No. . . ."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.7,
      "end": 144.08,
      "text": "Sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 144.85,
      "end": 146.1,
      "text": "He got snotty,"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.28,
      "end": 146.92,
      "text": "but so did I. . . ."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.76,
      "end": 149.5,
      "text": "He's nursing a gambler's-war pipe-dream. . . ."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.22,
      "end": 150.62,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.08,
      "end": 152.56,
      "text": "we didn't kiss when we parted."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.48,
      "end": 155.48,
      "text": "I declared my weight and walked out on him. . . ."
    },
    {
      "start": 156.48,
      "end": 157.8,
      "text": "That's something for you to worry about. . . ."
    },
    {
      "start": 158.7,
      "end": 158.98,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 159.18,
      "end": 159.296,
      "text": "'Bye.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 160.86,
      "end": 163.3,
      "text": "He put the telephone down and leaned back in his chair again."
    },
    {
      "start": 164.32,
      "end": 166.78,
      "text": "Effie Perine came from behind him and stood at his side.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 166.96,
      "end": 167.9,
      "text": "She demanded:"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.5,
      "end": 170.72,
      "text": "\"Do you think you know where she is,"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.8,
      "end": 171.0,
      "text": "Sam?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 171.63,
      "end": 173.18,
      "text": "\"I know where she went,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 173.4,
      "end": 175.12,
      "text": "he replied in a grudging tone."
    },
    {
      "start": 175.92,
      "end": 176.16,
      "text": "\"Where?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 176.84,
      "end": 177.52,
      "text": "She was excited."
    },
    {
      "start": 178.62,
      "end": 180.02,
      "text": "\"Down to the boat you saw burning.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 180.7,
      "end": 183.92,
      "text": "Her eyes opened until their brown was surrounded by white.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 184.68,
      "end": 185.44,
      "text": "\"You went down there.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 185.82,
      "end": 186.68,
      "text": "It was not a question."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.56,
      "end": 188.02,
      "text": "\"I did not,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 188.28,
      "end": 189.0,
      "text": "Spade said."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.6,
      "end": 190.24,
      "text": "\"Sam,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 190.76,
      "end": 191.77,
      "text": "she cried angrily,"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.08,
      "end": 192.64,
      "text": "\"she may be—\""
    },
    {
      "start": 193.62,
      "end": 194.54,
      "text": "\"She went down there,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 194.66,
      "end": 195.98,
      "text": "he said in a surly voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 196.54,
      "end": 197.36,
      "text": "\"She wasn't taken."
    },
    {
      "start": 198.28,
      "end": 199.94,
      "text": "She went down there instead of to your"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.94,
      "end": 201.88,
      "text": "house when she learned the boat was in."
    },
    {
      "start": 202.7,
      "end": 202.82,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.0,
      "end": 203.8,
      "text": "what the hell?"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.84,
      "end": 206.52,
      "text": "Am I supposed to run around after my"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.52,
      "end": 208.42,
      "text": "clients begging them to let me help them?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 209.18,
      "end": 209.58,
      "text": "\"But, Sam,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 209.78,
      "end": 211.78,
      "text": "when I told you the boat was on fire!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 212.98,
      "end": 215.5,
      "text": "\"That was at noon and I had a date with Polhaus",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 215.7,
      "end": 216.7,
      "text": "and another with Bryan.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 217.8,
      "end": 219.8,
      "text": "She glared at him between tightened lids.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 220.544,
      "end": 221.18,
      "text": "\"Sam Spade,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 221.34,
      "end": 221.84,
      "text": "she said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.0,
      "end": 222.72,
      "text": "\"you're the most"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.14,
      "end": 226.22,
      "text": "contemptible man God ever made when you want to be."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.42,
      "end": 229.42,
      "text": "Because she did something without confiding"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.42,
      "end": 229.76,
      "text": "in you"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.84,
      "end": 233.46,
      "text": "you'd sit here and do nothing when you know she's in danger,"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.6,
      "end": 235.0,
      "text": "when you know she might be—\""
    },
    {
      "start": 235.936,
      "end": 237.34,
      "text": "Spade's face flushed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 237.34,
      "end": 239.04,
      "text": "He said stubbornly:"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.06,
      "end": 242.32,
      "text": "\"She's pretty capable of taking care of herself and she"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.4,
      "end": 244.22,
      "text": "knows where to come for help when she"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.22,
      "end": 246.4,
      "text": "thinks she needs it, and when it suits her.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 247.52,
      "end": 247.9,
      "text": "\"That's spite,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 248.2,
      "end": 251.8,
      "text": "the girl cried, \"and that's all it is!"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.8,
      "end": 254.58,
      "text": "You're sore because she did something on her own hook,"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.72,
      "end": 255.26,
      "text": "without telling you."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.12,
      "end": 259.28,
      "text": "Why shouldn't she? You're not so damned honest,"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.68,
      "end": 261.46,
      "text": "and you haven't been so much on the level"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.46,
      "end": 263.38,
      "text": "with her, that she should trust you"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.36,
      "end": 263.78,
      "text": "completely.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 264.76,
      "end": 267.1,
      "text": "*Spade said: \"That's enough of that.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 267.74,
      "end": 268.86,
      "text": "His tone brought",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 268.88,
      "end": 271.94,
      "text": "a brief uneasy glint into her hot eyes, but she"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.94,
      "end": 274.94,
      "text": "tossed her head and the glint vanished. Her mouth"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.08,
      "end": 276.2,
      "text": "was drawn taut and small."
    }
  ],
  "corrected": "claude"
}